original_title: Mrs. India INC rocks Colombo with Gala night in Colombo
original_body_lines: COLOMBO(New 1st):The Gala night of the beauty pageant Mrs. India INC was held yesterday in Colombo.
The event's glamour was elevated by Former Indian Cricketer and Film Star, S. Sreesanth.
Mrs. India Inc, the most glamorous beauty pageant for married women in India is hosting thier 4th season right here in Sri Lanka.

Among the exciting and adventurous events organized for the contestants, a Gala Party was held in Colombo yesterday. Indian Former Cricketer and Actor, S. Sreesanth along with other influencers participated for this event.
The families of the contestants also participated in this event.
The Grand Final of sophisticated Mrs India INC will take place tomorrow at Colombo.
Legends 966 and TV1 are the proud media partners for Mrs. India Inc Season 4. So stay tuned for more updates on Mrs.India INC.
